量理科係判斷嗰項發明或者發現有無直接效用，對價值觀同審美需求較低，變相可以更快轉換成資本(賺錢)。<br />\n<br />\n我會話係意識形態問題多於科目本身。"},{"pid":"348792bd028186dd346000b5ab4b70dea97f1b68","tid":2238913,"uid":201031,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T18:15:01.000Z","msg":"住香港讀咩都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89190f3dd0b374d9768ec955062e7311d66eac47","tid":2238913,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"娛樂囉"},{"pid":"d8d67e769014fbdeaf977b97c1a5a45609241685","tid":2238913,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b024b3c9f5ed51e3e69bdf1debf9d4cca1edca69","tid":2238913,"uid":44722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n文科mk同偽文青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理科毒撚自閉仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"今時今日香港立法會系<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">「一個文科出身既議員都冇」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算香港人投票送入去都被DQ曬<br />\n<br />\n游蕙禎（中文系）<br />\n羅冠聰（文件研究）<br />\n<br />\n或者文人風骨不為5斗米折腰<br />\n<br />\n朱凱迪（英文系）"},{"pid":"5c1c1f06ed7e94df68a46d0cdcc5d01fa50155c8","tid":2238913,"uid":366099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"law算唔算文科？"},{"pid":"d2439eb4c47aec0c75d4c5160ee2d9bc8a8c90be","tid":2238913,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c1c1f06ed7e94df68a46d0cdcc5d01fa50155c8","tid":2238913,"uid":366099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"law算唔算文科？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"掉翻轉問 讀law嘅憑咩認為自己唔係讀緊文科？law有咩咁超然？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b438345c26fcca2ea55f81d5c14811eed8713c9","tid":2238913,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2439eb4c47aec0c75d4c5160ee2d9bc8a8c90be"