s://www.google.com/amp/s/www.cnbc.com/amp/2018/02/20/mark-cuban-philosophy-degree-will-be-worth-more-than-computer-science.html</a>"},{"pid":"77e46b504d9d4bc50d9bc438b1f77de55dd1c88d","tid":2238913,"uid":60321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"文科咁多種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過就算講文學/藝術/音樂/電影依啲<br />\n當有特別既諗法, 但無途徑表達出黎<br />\n都會好需要依啲表達思想既工具表達出黎<br />\n<br />\n一啲好有啟發性/ 改變社會既諗法<br />\n如果你講到一舊舊, 人地只會覺得你純粹搵野屌<br />\n改變社會有時可能只係差個表達角度扭一扭轉<br />\n<br />\n又例如你嬲或者你話一個人嬲, 但係點既嬲法？<br />\n係想毀天滅地既嬲 / 係暗處滋生出黎既嬲 / 定係好尖銳既嬲？<br />\n<br />\n好似我打左咁大段廢話<br />\n有人用幾句更簡而精既說話就講完<br />\n所以有時好羡慕藝術文學音樂好既人<br />\n可以將內在既諗法 變成一啲好實在既野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔識9up下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6df9fe89d5433a24c0ba996254542fb8b8ba8b","tid":2238913,"uid":303352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"假設問題:<br />\n如果全世界都無咗文學系、哲學系、歷史系，十年之後社會會唔會變差?<br />\n如果有，係點變法?"},{"pid":"864aec72104e56ecb8affb8b7edf8aaf80792a28","tid":2238913,"uid":366245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:32:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2c140fb7301700ddb578f66ceec5a3378d42f8a","tid":2238913,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d8d67e769014fbdeaf977b97c1a5a45609241685","tid":2238913,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b024b3c9f5ed51e3e69bdf1debf9d4cca1edca69","tid":2238913,"uid":44722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T15:03:16.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n文科mk同偽文青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理科毒撚自閉仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"今時今日香港立法會系<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">「一個文科出身既議員都冇」</span></span><br />